{"tid":1488892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<821>咁撚大件事冇人講 全撚同我入嚟！","createTime":"2019-08-19T17:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T08:18:21.000Z","uid":290804,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"28f0d028e3f53a3b3d16c630fa695326116c8a3f","tid":1488892,"uid":290804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:25:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">元朗721恐怖襲擊事件</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">已經過去一個月</span><br />\n<br />\n我哋仲未得到任何合理回答 黑社會仍然逍遙法外<br />\n<br />\n除此之外我哋仲有好多嘢都未得到合理回答！<br />\n<br />\n香港人係善忘 冇錯 但係 你地唔好唔記得 <br />\n我地有六百幾七百人被捕 好多手足受傷 多不勝數 <br />\n(骨折 斷牙 爆眼 腦出血 內出血 斬傷 仲有佢哋6個）<br />\n你哋係咪甘心忘記佢？係咪以為1,700,000淋住雨咁行<br />\n黑警冇射催淚彈 咁樣就代表勝利？<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚係啊！</span></span>呢樣只係代表我哋香港人堅持！<br />\n<br />\n回想初衷 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></span>我哋要嘅事呢樣野 唔係其他 唔好俾其他事分心 就算真係分咗心 睇過笑過J過 就返嚟<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權 一步不讓</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n係 冇錯呢兩日係有啲插曲令大家分心左 但係完咗就做翻主線任務 繼續闖下去 咁樣先係識分黑白有良知嘅香港人！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣組</span></span> <br />\n-好多對家嘅柒野 衰撚左嘅野 需要大家無限放大 分享出去！<br />\n-日程表 每天keep住登上熱門 <br />\n-連儂牆 保持更新 撕一貼百<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人人勇武</span></span><br />\n勇武 唔係分系分派 依家離開咗自己屋企門口就已經冇地方再係安全 人人一套保護自己嘅裝備 合法保護自己人身安全 需要嘅時候先裝上身<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非完係時候諗下死線<br />\n821  元朗靜坐 <br />\n822 中學生集會 <br />\n823 人鏈 會計界<br />\n824 觀塘遊行<br />\n825 荃葵青遊行<br />\n827 林鄭主持行政會議開會<br />\n831 民陣</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢場運動 並沒有所謂嘅熱潮退減 我哋大大聲同出邊嘅人講 我哋而家吸一啖氣 愈戰愈強 無人可以打倒我哋香港人!除咗你自己放棄你自己!<br />\nSORRY 你放棄自己 我哋咁多位兄弟姊妹扶返起你<br />\n繼續向目標進發！<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好忘記我哋約咗係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">煲底</span></strong></span>要做咩！想相認 就繼續出發 唔好氣餒 唔好輸比黑暗 所有有良知嘅人 加油！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">香港人爬山</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">各有各做</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚分化</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚割蓆</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚譴責</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚會輸</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">時代革命</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">卻一不可</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"7a23bb4a81afaf173baa0f1d739277b5f828c660","tid":1488892,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:27:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0867c79f33df2828a20deb31a7506b7570c2a76c","tid":1488892,"uid":163271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:27:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a80b109eec36f8db6328941592f6ada9ff6e83f1","tid":1488892,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:29:28.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-lin